### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5232
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/profile
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Register - Customer (Tự động gán role customer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@test.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "fullName": "Nguyễn Văn A"
}

###

### 3. Register - User khác
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user2@test.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "fullName": "Trần Thị B"
}

###

### 4. Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@test.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### 5. Login Admin (Được tạo tự động khi seed)
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@pawra.com",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

###

### 6. Get Profile (Cần Authentication)
# Sau khi login, copy token và paste vào variable @token ở đầu file
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7. Get All Account Roles (Chỉ Admin)
# Sau khi login admin, copy token và paste vào variable @token
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accountrole/all
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 8. Get Profile với token trực tiếp (Alternative)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

###
